txt.en: You experienced all that Umbar has to offer. You survived the treacherous Shield Isles, the shoreline of the Cape of Umbar, and even the city of Umbar Baharbêl. You are the consummate traveller, explorer, and purveyor of all things in this foreign land.
You slew many enemies, explored thoroughly, and quested widely within Umbar Baharbêl.
You slew many enemies, explored thoroughly, and quested widely across the Shield Isles.
You slew many enemies, explored thoroughly, and quested widely across the Cape of Umbar.
Complete: Deeds of the Shield Isles
